	pre-inflation             		inflation                       	post-inflation
	----------------------------------->	----------------------------------->	----------------------------------->
	fixed interest (asset)								variable interest (credit)
	interest rate will be increased		political interest will be increased	interest rate will be decreased
	money supply will be decreased							money supply will be increased





